The [[Hierophant]] Bio-titan with this upgrade gains a Transport capacity of 20 models, and friendly units chosen from //Codex: Tyranids// may embark and disembark from it as though it was a Vehicle with the [[Transport]] type and [[Assault Vehicle]] special rule.